column2: Question
If the election for governor were being held today, and the candidates were Republican Brian Kemp, Democrat Stacey Abrams, Libertarian Shane Hazel and Independent Al Bartel, for whom would you vote?
If the election for U.S. Senate were being held today, and the candidates were Republican Herschel Walker, Democrat Raphael Warnock and Libertarian Chase Oliver, for whom would you vote?
If the election for Lt. Governor were being held today, and the candidates were Republican Burt Jones, Democrat Charlie Bailey and Libertarian Ryan Graham, for whom would you vote?
If the election for Secretary of State were being held today, and the candidates were Republican Brad Raffensperger, Democrat Bee Nguyen and Libertarian Ted Metz, for whom would you vote?
If the election for Secretary of State were being held today, and the candidates were Republican Chris Carr, Democrat Jennifer Jordan  and Libertarian Martin Cowen, for whom would you vote?
If the election were today, would you want to see the Republican Party or the Democratic Party win control of the U.S. Congress?
Do you approve or disapprove of the way Joe Biden is handling his job as president?
Regardless of who you are voting for, do you like or dislike how Herschel Walker handles himself personally?
Regardless of who you are voting for, do you like or dislike how Raphael Warnock handles himself personally?
Who do you trust more on the economy and cost-of-living?
Who do you trust more on preserving democracy?
Who do you trust more on defending your values?
Who do you trust more on abortion?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Stacey Abrams?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Brian Kemp?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Raphael Warnock?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Herschel Walker?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Joe Biden?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Donald Trump?
Would you say Herschel Walker is honest or not?
Would you say Herschel Walker has good leadership skills or not?
Would you say Herschel Walker understands the issues he will deal with in office or not?
Would you say Herschel Walker cares about average Georgians or not?
Would you say Raphael Warnock is honest or not?
Would you say Raphael Warnock has good leadership skills or not?
Would you say Raphael Warnock understands the issues he will deal with in office or not?
Would you say Raphael Warnock cares about average Georgians or not?
